{{Time zones of Africa}}
'''Cape Verde Time''' ('''CVT''') is a [[time zone]] used by the Atlantic island nation of [[Cape Verde]]. The zone is one hour behind UTC ([[UTC-1]]).

[[Daylight saving time]] is not observed in this time zone.

