'''São Nicolau Airport''' ({{lang-pt|Aeródromo de São Nicolau}}) {{Airport codes|SNE|GVSN}} is the domestic airport of the island of [[São Nicolau, Cape Verde|São Nicolau]], [[Cape Verde]]. It is located 3 km north of the village [[Preguiça, São Nicolau|Preguiça]] and about 3&nbsp;km south of the island capital [[Ribeira Brava, Cape Verde|Ribeira Brava]]. Its runway is 1,400 meters and is categorized 3C.<ref name=asa>[https://www.asa.cv/aerodromos/aerodromo-de-sao-nicolau/ Aeródromo de São Nicolau], Aeroportos e Segurança Aérea {{pt icon}}</ref>
